properties.Name: EncounterTestEventType
properties.Description:
A type of encounter event that is associated with an encounter test.

Ex:
- Test completed
- Test Performed
- Test Sent to Lab
- Test Analyzed
- Test Results Returned
- Test Results Conveyed To Patient
- Test Results Sent to Payer
- Test canceled
- Re-test Requested
